<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/7/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/7/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "perencanaan tenaga kerja makro, dan" .
