<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "penduduk dan tenaga kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
