<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "kesempatan kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "pelatihan kerja termasuk kompetensi kerja," .
