<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "pengupahan dan kesejahteraan tenaga kerja, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "jaminan sosial tenaga kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/1/point/h/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Informasi ketenagakerjaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), diperoleh dari semua pihak yang terkait, baik instansi pemerintah maupun swasta." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara memperoleh informasi ketenagakerjaan dan penyusunan serta pelaksanaan perencanaan tenaga kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/8/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab> legal:babSetHasBab <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/5> legal:babHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/5> legal:babHasTitle "PELATIHAN KERJA" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/5> legal:babHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9> legal:pasalHasKey 9 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja diselenggarakan dan diarahkan untuk membekali, meningkatkan, dan mengembangkan kompetensi kerja guna meningkatkan kemampuan, produktivitas, dan kesejahteraan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/9/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10> legal:pasalHasKey 10 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja dilaksanakan dengan memperhatikan kebutuhan pasar kerja dan dunia usaha, baik di da-lam maupun di luar hubungan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja diselenggarakan berdasarkan program pelatihan yang mengacu pada standar kompetensi kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja dapat dilakukan secara berjenjang." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara penetapan standar kompetensi kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/10/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11> legal:pasalHasKey 11 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap tenaga kerja berhak untuk memperoleh dan/atau meningkatkan dan/atau mengembangkan kompetensi kerja sesuai dengan bakat, minat, dan kemampuannya melalui pelatihan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/11/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12> legal:pasalHasKey 12 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha bertanggung jawab atas peningkatan dan/atau pengembangan kompetensi pekerjanya melalui pelatihan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Peningkatan dan/atau pengembangan kompetensi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diwajibkan bagi pengusaha yang memenuhi persyaratan yang diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh memiliki kesempatan yang sama untuk mengikuti pelatihan kerja sesuai dengan bi-dang tugasnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/12/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13> legal:pasalHasKey 13 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja diselenggarakan oleh lembaga pelatihan kerja pemerintah dan/atau lembaga pelatihan kerja swasta." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja dapat diselenggarakan di tempat pelatihan atau tempat kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga pelatihan kerja pemerintah sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (l) dalam menyelenggarakan pe-latihan kerja dapat bekerja sama dengan swasta." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/13/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14> legal:pasalHasKey 14 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga pelatihan kerja swasta dapat berbentuk badan hukum Indonesia atau perorangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga pelatihan kerja swasta sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) wajib memperoleh izin atau men daftar ke instansi yang bertanggung jawab di bidang ketenagakerjaan di kabupaten/kota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga pelatihan kerja yang diselenggarakan oleh instansi pemerintah mendaftarkan kegiatannya kepada instansi yang bertanggung jawab di bidang ketenagakerjaan di kabupaten/kota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara perizinan dan pendaftaran lembaga pelatihan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dan ayat (3) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/14/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15> legal:pasalHasKey 15 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Penyelenggara pelatihan kerja wajib memenuhi persyaratan :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "tersedianya tenaga kepelatihan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "adanya kurikulum yang sesuai dengan tingkat pelatihan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "tersedianya sarana dan prasarana pelatihan kerja, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "tersedianya dana bagi kelangsungan kegiatan penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/15/version/0/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16> legal:pasalHasKey 16 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga pelatihan kerja swasta yang telah memperoleh izin dan lembaga pelatihan kerja pemerintah yang telah terdaftar dapat memperoleh akreditasi dari lembaga akreditasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga akreditasi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) bersifat independen terdiri atas unsur masya rakat dan pemerintah ditetapkan dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Organisasi dan tata kerja lembaga akreditasi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Kepu tusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/16/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17> legal:pasalHasKey 17 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Instansi yang bertanggung jawab di bidang ketenagakerjaan di kabupaten/kota dapat menghentikan sementara pelaksanaan penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja, apabila dalam pelaksanaannya ternyata :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "tidak sesuai dengan arah pelatihan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 9: dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "tidak memenuhi persyaratan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 15." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penghentian sementara pelaksanaan penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), disertai alasan dan saran perbaikan dan berlaku paling lama 6 (enam) bulan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penghentian sementara pelaksanaan penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja hanya dikenakan terhadap program pelatihan yang tidak memenuhi syarat sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 9 dan Pasal 15." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Bagi penyelenggara pelatihan kerja dalam waktu 6 (enam) bulan tidak memenuhi dan melengkapi saran per baikan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dikenakan sanksi penghentian program pelatihan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyelenggara pelatihan kerja yang tidak menaati dan tetap melaksanakan program pelatihan kerja yang telah dihentikan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (4) dikenakan sanksi pencabutan izin dan pembatalan pendaftaran penyelenggara pelatihan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/6/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara penghentian sementara, penghentian, pencabutan izin, dan pembatalan pen daftaran diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/version/0/ayat/6/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18> legal:pasalHasKey 18 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tenaga kerja berhak memperoleh pengakuan kompetensi kerja setelah mengikuti pelatihan kerja yang di selenggarakan lembaga pelatihan kerja pemerintah, lembaga pelatihan kerja swasta, atau pelatihan di tempat kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengakuan kompetensi kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dilakukan melalui sertifikasi kompe tensi kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Sertifikasi kompetensi kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dapat pula diikuti oleh tenaga kerja yang telah berpengalaman." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk melaksanakan sertifikasi kompetensi kerja dibentuk badan nasional sertifikasi profesi yang inde penden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembentukan badan nasional sertifikasi profesi yang independen sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (4) diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/18/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19> legal:pasalHasKey 19 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja bagi tenaga kerja penyandang cacat dilaksanakan dengan memperhatikan jenis, derajat kecacatan, dan kemampuan tenaga kerja penyandang cacat yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/19/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20> legal:pasalHasKey 20 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk mendukung peningkatan pelatihan kerja dalam rangka pembangunan ketenagakerjaan, dikembang kan satu sistem pelatihan kerja nasional yang merupakan acuan pelaksanaan pelatihan kerja di semua bidang dan/atau sektor." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai bentuk, mekanisme, dan kelembagaan sistem pelatihan kerja nasional sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/20/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21> legal:pasalHasKey 21 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelatihan kerja dapat diselenggarakan dengan sistem pemagangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/21/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22> legal:pasalHasKey 22 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemagangan dilaksanakan atas dasar perjanjian pemagangan antara peserta dengan pengusaha yang di buat secara tertulis." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian pemagangan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), sekurang- kurangnya memuat ketentuan hak dan kewajiban peserta dan pengusaha serta jangka waktu pemagangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemagangan yang diselenggarakan tidak melalui perjanjian pemagangan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), dianggap tidak sah dan status peserta berubah menjadi pekerja/buruh perusahaan yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23> legal:pasalHasKey 23 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tenaga kerja yang telah mengikuti program pemagangan berhak atas pengakuan kualifikasi kompetensi kerja dari perusahaan atau lembaga sertifikasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/23/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24> legal:pasalHasKey 24 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemagangan dapat dilaksanakan di perusahaan sendiri atau di tempat penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja, atau perusahaan lain, baik di dalam maupun di luar wilayah Indonesia." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/24/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25> legal:pasalHasKey 25 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemagangan yang dilakukan di luar wilayah Indonesia wajib mendapat izin dari Menteri atau pejabat yang ditunjuk." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk memperoleh izin sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), penyelenggara pemagangan harus ber bentuk badan hukum Indonesia sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara perizinan pemagangan di luar wilayah Indonesia sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (2), diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26> legal:pasalHasKey 26 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Penyelenggaraan pemagangan di luar wilayah Indonesia harus memperhatikan :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "harkat dan martabat bangsa Indonesia," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "penguasaan kompetensi yang lebih tinggi, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "perlindungan dan kesejahteraan peserta pemagangan, termasuk melaksanakan ibadahnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri atau pejabat yang ditunjuk dapat menghentikan pelaksanaan pemagangan di luar wilayah Indo nesia apabila di dalam pelaksanaannya ternyata tidak sesuai dengan ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat @)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27> legal:pasalHasKey 27 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0> .
