<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri dapat mewajibkan kepada perusahaan yang memenuhi persyaratan untuk melaksanakan program pemagangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam menetapkan persyaratan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), Menteri harus memperhatikan ke pentingan perusahaan, masyarakat, dan negara." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/27/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28> legal:pasalHasKey 28 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk memberikan saran dan pertimbangan dalam penetapan kebijakan serta melakukan koordinasi pela tihan kerja dan pemagangan dibentuk lembaga koordinasi pelatihan kerja nasional." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembentukan, keanggotaan, dan tata kerja lembaga koordinasi pelatihan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud da lam ayat (1), diatur dengan Keputusan Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29> legal:pasalHasKey 29 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemerintah Pusat dan/atau Pemerintah Daerah melakukan pembinaan pelatihan kerja dan pemagangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembinaan pelatihan kerja dan pemagangan ditujukan ke arah peningkatan relevansi, kualitas, dan efisien si penyelenggaraan pelatihan kerja dan produktivitas." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Peningkatan produktivitas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2), dilakukan melalui pengembangan buda ya produktif, etos kerja, teknologi, dan efisiensi kegiatan ekonomi, menuju terwujudnya produktivitas nasional." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30> legal:pasalHasKey 30 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk meningkatkan produktivitas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 29 ayat (2) dibentuk lembaga pro duktivitas yang bersifat nasional." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga produktivitas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) berbentuk jejaring kelembagaan pelayanan peningkatan produktivitas, yang bersifat lintas sektor maupun daerah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembentukan, keanggotaan, dan tata kerja lembaga produktivitas nasional sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), diatur dengan Keputusan Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab> legal:babSetHasBab <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/6> legal:babHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/6> legal:babHasTitle "PENEMPATAN TENAGA KERJA" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/6> legal:babHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31> legal:pasalHasKey 31 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap tenaga kerja mempunyai hak dan kesempatan yang sama untuk memilih, mendapatkan, atau pindah pekerjaan dan memperoleh penghasilan yang layak di dalam atau di luar negeri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/31/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32> legal:pasalHasKey 32 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penempatan tenaga kerja dilaksanakan berdasarkan asas terbuka, bebas, obyektif, serta adil, dan setara tanpa diskriminasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penempatan tenaga kerja diarahkan untuk menempatkan tenaga kerja pada jabatan yang tepat sesuai de ngan keahlian, keterampilan, bakat, minat, dan kemampuan dengan memperhatikan harkat, martabat, hak asasi, dan perlindungan hukum." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penempatan tenaga kerja dilaksanakan dengan memperhatikan pemerataan kesempatan kerja dan penye diaan tenaga kerja sesuai dengan kebutuhan program nasional dan daerah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/32/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
