<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "penempatan tenaga kerja di dalam negeri, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/b> .
