<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "penempatan tenaga kerja di luar negeri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/33/version/0/point/b/text> .
