<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penempatan tenaga kerja oleh pelaksana sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 35 ayat (1) dilakukan dengan memberikan pelayanan penempatan tenaga kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pelayanan penempatan tenaga kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) bersifat terpadu dalam satu sistem penempatan tenaga kerja yang meliputi unsur-unsur :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "pencari kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
