<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "lowongan pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
