<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "mekanisme antar kerja, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "kelembagaan penempatan tenaga kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Unsur-unsur sistem penempatan tenaga kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dapat dilaksanakan secara terpisah yang ditujukan untuk terwujudnya penempatan tenaga kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
