<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/7> legal:babHasTitle "PERLUASAN KESEMPATAN KERJA" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/7> legal:babHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
