<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tenaga kerja asing dilarang menduduki jabatan yang mengurusi personalia dan/atau jabatan-jabatan ter tentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Jabatan-jabatan tertentu sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/46/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
