<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemberi kerja wajib membayar kompensasi atas setiap tenaga kerja asing yang dipekerjakannya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kewajiban membayar kompensasi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) tidak berlaku bagi instansi pe merintah, perwakilan negara asing, badan- badan internasional, lembaga sosial, lembaga keagamaan, dan jabatan- jabatan tertentu di lembaga pendidikan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai jabatan-jabatan tertentu di lembaga pendidikan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai besarnya kompensasi dan penggunaannya diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/47/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/48> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/48> legal:pasalHasKey 48 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/48> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/48/version/0> .
