<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49> legal:pasalHasKey 49 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai penggunaan tenaga kerja asing serta pelaksanaan pendidikan dan pelatihan tenaga kerja pendamping diatur dengan Keputusan Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/49/version/0/text> .
