<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja yang dipersyaratkan secara tertulis dilaksanakan sesuai dengan peraturan perundang undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
