<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja yang dibuat secara tertulis sekurang kurangnya memuat :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
