<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "nama, alamat perusahaan, dan jenis usaha," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "nama, jenis kelamin, umur, dan alamat pekerja/buruh," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "jabatan atau jenis pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "tempat pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "besarnya upah dan cara pembayarannya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "syarat syarat kerja yang memuat hak dan kewajiban pengusaha dan pekerja/buruh," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "mulai dan jangka waktu berlakunya perjanjian kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "tempat dan tanggal perjanjian kerja dibuat, dan Ii. tanda tangan para pihak dalam perjanjian kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/h> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/point/h/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan dalam perjanjian kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) huruf e dan f, tidak boleh ber-tentangan dengan peraturan perusahaan, perjanjian kerja bersama, dan peraturan perundang undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dibuat sekurang kurangnya rangkap 2 (dua), yang mempunyai kekuatan hukum yang sama, serta pekerja/buruh dan pengusaha masing masing mendapat 1 (satu) perjanjian kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55> legal:pasalHasKey 55 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja tidak dapat ditarik kembali dan/atau diubah, kecuali atas persetujuan para pihak." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/55/version/0/text> .
