<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja dibuat untuk waktu tertentu atau untuk waktu tidak tertentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Perjanjian kerja untuk waktu tertentu sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (l) didasarkan atas :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Jangka waktu, atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "selesainya suatu pekerjaan tertentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/57> .
