<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/62/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/62/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/62/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Apabila salah satu pihak mengakhiri hubungan kerja sebelum berakhirnya jangka waktu yang ditetapkan dalam perjanjian kerja waktu tertentu, atau berakhirnya hubungan kerja bukan karena ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 61 ayat (1), pihak yang mengakhiri hubungan kerja diwajibkan membayar ganti rugi kepada pihak lainnya sebesar upah pekerja/buruh sampai batas waktu berakhirnya jangka waktu perjanjian kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/62/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/62/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63> legal:pasalHasKey 63 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal perjanjian kerja waktu tidak tertentu dibuat secara lisan, maka pengusaha wajib membuat surat pengangkatan bagi pekerja/buruh yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Surat pengangkatan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), sekurang kurangnya memuat keterangan :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "nama dan alamat pekerja/buruh," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "tanggal mulai bekerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "jenis pekerjaan, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "besarnya upah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/63/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64> legal:pasalHasKey 64 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perusahaan dapat menyerahkan sebagian pelaksanaan pekerjaan kepada perusahaan lainnya melalui perjanjian pemborongan pekerjaan atau penyediaan jasa pekerja/buruh yang dibuat secara tertulis." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/64/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65> legal:pasalHasKey 65 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyerahan sebagian pelaksanaan pekerjaan kepada perusahaan lain dilaksanakan melalui perjanjian pem borongan pekerjaan yang dibuat secara tertulis." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerjaan yang dapat diserahkan kepada perusahaan lain sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) harus memenuhi syarat-syarat sebagai berikut :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "dilakukan secara terpisah dari kegiatan utama," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "dilakukan dengan perintah langsung atau tidak langsung dari pemberi pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "merupakan kegiatan penunjang perusahaan secara keseluruhan, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "tidak menghambat proses produksi secara langsung." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perusahaan lain sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) harus berbentuk badan hukum." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perlindungan kerja dan syarat-syarat kerja bagi pekerja/buruh pada perusahaan lain sebagaimana dimak-sud dalam ayat (2) sekurang- kurangnya sama dengan perlindungan kerja dan syarat-syarat kerja pada perusahaan pemberi pekerjaan atau sesuai dengan peraturan perundang- undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perubahan dan/atau penambahan syarat-syarat sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur lebih lanjut dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/6/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hubungan kerja dalam pelaksanaan pekerjaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dalam perjanjian kerja secara tertulis antara perusahaan lain dan pekerja/buruh yang dipekerjakannya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/6/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/7> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/7> legal:ayatHasKey 7 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/7/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hubungan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (6) dapat didasarkan atas perjanjian kerja waktu tidak tertentu atau perjanjian kerja waktu tertentu apabila memenuhi persyaratan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 59." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/7> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/7/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/8> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/8> legal:ayatHasKey 8 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/8/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dan ayat (3) tidak terpenuhi, maka demi hukum status hubungan kerja pekerja/buruh dengan perusahaan penerima pemborongan beralih menjadi hubungan kerja pekerja/buruh dengan perusahaan pemberi pekerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/8> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/8/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/9> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/9> legal:ayatHasKey 9 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/9/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal hubungan kerja beralih ke perusahaan pemberi pekerjaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (8), maka hubungan kerja pekerja/buruh dengan pemberi pekerjaan sesuai dengan hubungan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (7)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/9> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/65/version/0/ayat/9/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66> legal:pasalHasKey 66 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh dari perusahaan penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh tidak boleh digunakan oleh pemberi kerja untuk melaksanakan kegiatan pokok atau kegiatan yang berhubungan langsung dengan proses produksi, kecuali untuk kegiatan jasa penunjang atau kegiatan yang tidak berhubungan langsung dengan proses produksi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh untuk kegiatan jasa penunjang atau kegiatan yang tidak berhubungan lang-sung dengan proses produksi harus memenuhi syarat sebagai berikut :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "adanya hubungan kerja antara pekerja/buruh dan perusahaan penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "perjanjian kerja yang berlaku dalam hubungan kerja sebagaimana dimaksud pada huruf a adalah perjanjian kerja untuk waktu tertentu yang memenuhi persyaratan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 59 dan/atau perjanjian kerja waktu tidak tertentu yang dibuat secara tertulis dan ditandatangani oleh kedua belah pihak," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "perlindungan upah dan kesejahteraan, syarat-syarat kerja, serta perselisihan yang timbul menjadi tanggung jawab perusahaan penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "perjanjian antara perusahaan pengguna jasa pekerja/buruh dan perusahaan lain yang bertindak sebagai perusahaan penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh dibuat secara tertulis dan wajib memuat pasal-pasal sebagaimana dimaksud dalam undang-undang ini." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh merupakan bentuk usaha yang berbadan hukum dan memiliki izin dari instansi yang bertanggung jawab di bidang ketenagakerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), ayat (2) huruf a, huruf b, dan huruf d serta ayat (3) tidak terpenuhi, maka demi hukum status hubungan kerja antara pekerja/buruh dan perusahaan penyedia jasa pekerja/buruh beralih menjadi hubungan kerja antara pekerja/buruh dan perusahaan pemberi pekerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/66/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab> legal:babSetHasBab <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10> legal:babHasKey 10 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10> legal:babHasTitle "PERLINDUNGAN, PENGUPAHAN, DAN KESEJAHTERAAN" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10> legal:babHasBagianSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kesatu Perlindungan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasParagrafSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/1> legal:paragrafHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/1> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 1 Penyandang Cacat" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/1> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67> legal:pasalHasKey 67 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan tenaga kerja penyandang cacat wajib memberikan perlindungan sesuai dengan jenis dan derajat kecacatannya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemberian perlindungan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dilaksanakan sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/67/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 2 Anak" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68> legal:pasalHasKey 68 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha dilarang mempekerjakan anak." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/68/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69> legal:pasalHasKey 69 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 68 dapat dikecualikan bagi anak yang berumur antara 13 (tiga belas) tahun sampai dengan 15 (lima belas) tahun untuk melakukan pekerjaan ringan sepanjang tidak mengganggu perkembangan dan kesehatan fisik, mental, dan sosial." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan anak pada pekerjaan ringan sebagai-mana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) ha-rus memenuhi persyaratan :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "izin tertulis dari orang tua atau wali," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "perjanjian kerja antara pengusaha dengan orang tua atau wali," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "waktu kerja maksimum 3 (tiga) jam," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "dilakukan pada siang hari dan tidak mengganggu waktu sekolah," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "adanya hubungan kerja yang jelas, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "menerima upah sesuai dengan ketentuan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/2/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) huruf a, b, f, dan g dikecualikan bagi anak yang bekerja pada usaha keluarganya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/69/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70> legal:pasalHasKey 70 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anak dapat melakukan pekerjaan di tempat kerja yang merupakan bagian dari kurikulum pendidikan atau pelatihan yang disahkan oleh pejabat yang berwenang." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anak sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) paling sedikit berumur 14 (empat belas) tahun." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerjaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dapat dilakukan dengan syarat :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "diberi petunjuk yang jelas tentang cara pelaksanaan pekerjaan serta bimbingan dan pengawasan dalam melaksanakan pekerjaan, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "diberi perlindungan keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/70/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71> .
