<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anak dapat melakukan pekerjaan untuk mengembangkan bakat dan minatnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan anak sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) wajib memenuhi syarat :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "di bawah pengawasan langsung dari orang tua atau wali," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "waktu kerja paling lama 3 (tiga) jam sehari, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "kondisi dan lingkungan kerja tidak mengganggu perkembangan fisik, mental, sosial, dan waktu sekolah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai anak yang bekerja untuk mengembangkan bakat dan minat sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/71/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72> legal:pasalHasKey 72 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal anak dipekerjakan bersama-sama dengan pekerja/buruh dewasa, maka tempat kerja anak harus dipisahkan dari tempat kerja pekerja/buruh dewasa." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/72/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73> legal:pasalHasKey 73 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anak dianggap bekerja bilamana berada di tempat kerja, kecuali dapat dibuktikan sebaliknya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/73/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74> legal:pasalHasKey 74 .
