<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Siapapun dilarang mempekerjakan dan melibatkan anak pada pekerjaan- pekerjaan yang terburuk." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerjaan-pekerjaan yang terburuk yang dimaksud dalam ayat (1) meliputi:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "segala pekerjaan dalam bentuk perbudakan atau sejenisnya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "segala pekerjaan yang memanfaatkan, menyediakan, atau menawarkan anak untuk pelacuran, produksi pornografi, pertunjukan porno, atau perjudian," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "segala pekerjaan yang memanfaatkan, menyediakan, atau melibatkan anak untuk produksi dan perdagangan minuman keras, narkotika, psikotropika, dan zat adiktif lainnya, dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "semua pekerjaan yang membahayakan kesehatan, keselamatan, atau moral anak." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Jenis-jenis pekerjaaan yang membahayakan kesehatan, keselamatan, atau moral anak sebagaimana di-maksud dalam ayat (2) huruf d ditetapkan dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/74/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
