<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemerintah berkewajiban melakukan upaya penanggulangan anak yang bekerja di luar hubungan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/75/version/0/ayat/2> .
