<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh perempuan yang berumur kurang dari 18 (delapan belas) tahun dilarang dipekerjakan antara pukul 23.00 sampai dengan pukul 07.00." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha dilarang mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh perempuan hamil yang menurut keterangan dokter berbahaya bagi kesehatan dan keselamatan kandungannya maupun dirinya apabila bekerja antara pukul 23.00 sampai dengan pukul 07.00." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh perempuan antara pukul 23.00 sampai dengan pukul 07.00 wajib :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "memberikan makanan dan minuman bergizi, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "menjaga kesusilaan dan keamanan selama di tempat kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha wajib menyediakan angkutan antar jemput bagi pekerja/buruh perempuan yang berangkat dan pulang bekerja antara pukul 23.00 sampai dengan pukul 05.00." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (3) dan ayat (4) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/4> legal:paragrafHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/4> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 4 Waktu Kerja" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/4> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77> legal:pasalHasKey 77 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pengusaha wajib melaksanakan ketentuan waktu kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Waktu kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) meliputi :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "7 (tujuh) jam 1 (satu) hari dan 40 (empat puluh) jam 1 (satu) minggu untuk 6 (enam) hari kerja dalam 1 (satu) minggu, atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "8 (delapan) jam 1 (satu) hari dan 40 (empat puluh) jam 1 (satu) minggu untuk 5 (lima) hari kerja dalam 1 (satu) minggu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan waktu kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) tidak berlaku bagi sektor usaha atau peker-jaan tertentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai waktu kerja pada sektor usaha atau pekerjaan tertentu sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (3) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/77/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78> legal:pasalHasKey 78 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh melebihi waktu kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 77 ayat (2) harus memenuhi syarat :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "ada persetujuan pekerja/buruh yang bersangkutan, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "waktu kerja lembur hanya dapat dilakukan paling banyak 3 (tiga) jam dalam 1 (satu) hari dan 14 (empat belas) jam dalam 1 (satu) minggu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh melebihi waktu kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) wajib membayar upah kerja lembur." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan waktu kerja lembur sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) huruf b tidak berlaku bagi sektor usaha atau pekerjaan tertentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai waktu kerja lembur dan upah kerja lembur sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) dan ayat (3) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/78/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79> legal:pasalHasKey 79 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha wajib memberi waktu istirahat dan cuti kepada pekerja/buruh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Waktu istirahat dan cuti sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), meliputi :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "istirahat antara jam kerja, sekurang kurangnya setengah jam setelah bekerja selama 4 (empat) jam terus menerus dan waktu istirahat tersebut tidak termasuk jam kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "istirahat mingguan 1 (satu) hari untuk 6 (enam) hari kerja dalam 1 (satu) minggu atau 2 (dua) hari untuk 5 Jima) hari kerja dalam 1 (satu) minggu," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "cuti tahunan, sekurang kurangnya 12 (dua belas) hari kerja setelah pekerja/buruh yang bersangkutan bekerja selama 12 (dua belas) bulan secara terus menerus, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "istirahat panjang sekurang-kurangnya 2 (dua) bulan dan dilaksanakan pada tahun ketujuh dan kedelapan masing-masing 1 (satu) bulan bagi pekerja/buruh yang telah bekerja selama 6 (enam) tahun secara terus- menerus pada perusahaan yang sama dengan ketentuan pekerja/buruh tersebut tidak berhak lagi atas istirahat tahunannya dalam 2 (dua) tahun berjalan dan selanjutnya berlaku untuk setiap kelipatan masa kerja 6 (enam) tahun." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelaksanaan waktu istirahat tahunan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) huruf c diatur dalam perjanjian kerja, peraturan perusahaan, atau perjanjian kerja bersama." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hak istirahat panjang sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) huruf d hanya berlaku bagi pekerja/buruh yang bekerja pada perusahaan tertentu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perusahaan tertentu sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (4) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/79/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80> legal:pasalHasKey 80 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha wajib memberikan kesempatan yang secukupnya kepada pekerja/ buruh untuk melaksanakan ibadah yang diwajibkan oleh agamanya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/80/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81> legal:pasalHasKey 81 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh perempuan yang dalam masa haid merasakan sakit dan memberitahukan kepada pengusaha, tidak wajib bekerja pada hari pertama dan kedua pada waktu haid." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelaksanaan ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dalam perjanjian kerja, peraturan perusahaan, atau perjanjian kerja bersama." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/81/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82> legal:pasalHasKey 82 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh perempuan berhak memperoleh istirahat selama 1,5 (satu setengah) bulan sebelum saatnya melahirkan anak dan 1,5 (satu setengah) bulan sesudah melahirkan menurut perhitungan dokter kandungan atau bidan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh perempuan yang mengalami keguguran kandungan berhak memperoleh istirahat 1,5 (satu setengah) bulan atau sesuai dengan surat keterangan dokter kandungan atau bidan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/82/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83> legal:pasalHasKey 83 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh perempuan yang anaknya masih menyusu harus diberi kesempatan sepatutnya untuk menyusui anaknya jika hal itu harus dilakukan selama waktu kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/83/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84> legal:pasalHasKey 84 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh yang menggunakan hak waktu istirahat sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 79 ayat (2) huruf b, c, dan d, Pasal 80, dan Pasal 82 berhak mendapat upah penuh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/84/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85> legal:pasalHasKey 85 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pekerja/buruh tidak wajib bekerja pada hari-hari libur resmi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha dapat mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh untuk bekerja pada hari- hari libur resmi apabila jenis dan sifat pekerjaan tersebut harus dilaksanakan atau dijalankan secara terus- menerus atau pada keadaan lain berdasarkan kesepakatan antara pekerja/buruh dengan pengusaha." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang mempekerjakan pekerja/buruh yang melakukan pekerjaan pada hari libur resmi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) wajib membayar upah kerja lembur." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai jenis dan sifat pekerjaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/85/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/5> legal:paragrafHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/5> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 5 Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/1/paragraf/5> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86> legal:pasalHasKey 86 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh mempunyai hak untuk memperoleh perlindungan atas:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "moral dan kesusilaan: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "perlakuan yang sesuai dengan harkat dan martabat manusia serta nilai-nilai agama." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk melindungi keselamatan pekerja/buruh guna mewujudkan produktivitas kerja yang optimal diselenggarakan upaya keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Perlindungan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (2) dilaksanakan sesuai dengan peraturan perundang- undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/86/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
