<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kedua Pengupahan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88> legal:pasalHasKey 88 .
