<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh berhak memperoleh penghasilan yang memenuhi penghidupan yang layak bagi kemanusiaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk mewujudkan penghasilan yang memenuhi penghidupan yang layak bagi kemanusiaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), pemerintah menetapkan kebijakan pengupahan yang melindungi pekerja/buruh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Kebijakan pengupahan yang melindungi pekerja/buruh sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) meliputi :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah minimum," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah kerja lembur," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah tidak masuk kerja karena berhalangan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah tidak masuk kerja karena melakukan kegiatan lain di luar pekerjaannya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah karena menjalankan hak waktu istirahat kerjanya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "bentuk dan cara pembayaran upah," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "denda dan potongan upah," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "hal-hal yang dapat diperhitungkan dengan upah, Ii. struktur dan skala pengupahan yang proporsional, J- upah untuk pembayaran pesangon, dan k. upah untuk perhitungan pajak penghasilan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/h> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/3/point/h/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemerintah menetapkan upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (3) huruf a berdasarkan kebutuhan hidup layak dan dengan mem- perhatikan produktivitas dan pertumbuhan ekonomi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
