<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 88 ayat (3) huruf a dapat terdiri atas :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah minimum berdasarkan wilayah provinsi atau kabupaten/kota," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "upah minimum berdasarkan sektor pada wilayah provinsi atau kabupaten/kota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diarahkan kepada pencapaian kebutuhan hidup layak." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) ditetapkan oleh Gubernur dengan memperhatikan rekomendasi dari Dewan Pengupahan Provinsi dan/atau Bupati/Walikota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Komponen serta pelaksanaan tahapan pencapaian kebutuhan hidup layak sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/89/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90> legal:pasalHasKey 90 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha dilarang membayar upah lebih rendah dari upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 89." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Bagi pengusaha yang tidak mampu membayar upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 89 dapat dilakukan penangguhan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tata cara penangguhan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/90/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91> legal:pasalHasKey 91 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengaturan pengupahan yang ditetapkan atas kesepakatan antara pengusaha dan pekerja/buruh atau serikat pekerja/serikat buruh tidak boleh lebih rendah dari ketentuan pengupahan yang ditetapkan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal kesepakatan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) lebih rendah atau bertentangan dengan peraturan perundang-undangan, kesepakatan tersebut batal demi hukum, dan pengusaha wajib membayar upah pekerja/buruh menurut peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/91/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92> legal:pasalHasKey 92 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha menyusun struktur dan skala upah dengan memperhatikan golongan, jabatan, masa kerja, pendidikan, dan kompetensi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha melakukan peninjauan upah secara berkala dengan mem- perhatikan kemampuan perusahaan dan produktivitas." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai struktur dan skala upah sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/92/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93> legal:pasalHasKey 93 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Upah tidak dibayar apabila pekerja/buruh tidak melakukan pekerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) tidak berlaku, dan pengusaha wajib membayar upah apabila :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh sakit sehingga tidak dapat melakukan pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh perempuan yang sakit pada hari pertama dan kedua masa haidnya sehingga tidak dapat melakukan pekerjaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh tidak masuk bekerja karena pekerja/buruh menikah, menikahkan, mengkhitankan, membaptiskan anaknya, isteri melahirkan atau keguguran kandungan, suami atau isteri atau anak atau menantu atau orang tua atau mertua atau anggota keluarga dalam satu rumah meninggal dunia," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh tidak dapat melakukan pekerjaannya karena sedang menjalankan kewajiban terhadap negara," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh tidak dapat melakukan pekerjaannya karena menjalan- kan ibadah yang diperintahkan agamanya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh bersedia melakukan pekerjaan yang telah dijanjikan tetapi pengusaha tidak mempekerjakannya, baik karena kesalahan sendiri maupun halangan yang seharusnya dapat dihindari pengusaha," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh melaksanakan hak istirahat," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h> legal:pointHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh melaksanakan tugas serikat pekerja/serikat buruh atas persetujuan pengusaha, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1> legal:pointHasKey "1" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh melaksanakan tugas pendidikan dari perusahaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Upah yang dibayarkan kepada pekerja/buruh yang sakit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) huruf a sebagai berikut :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "untuk 4 (empat) bulan pertama, dibayar 10096 (seratus perseratus) dari upah," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "untuk 4 (empat) bulan kedua, dibayar 7590 (tujuh puluh lima perseratus) dari upah:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "untuk 4 (empat) bulan ketiga, dibayar 5096 (lima puluh perseratus) dari upah, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "untuk bulan selanjutnya dibayar 2596 (dua puluh lima perseratus) dari upah sebelum pemutusan hubungan kerja dilakukan oleh pengusaha." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Upah yang dibayarkan kepada pekerja/buruh yang tidak masuk bekerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) huruf c sebagai berikut :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "pekerja/buruh menikah, dibayar untuk selama 3 (tiga) hari:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "menikahkan anaknya, dibayar untuk selama 2 (dua) hari," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "mengkhitankan anaknya, dibayar untuk selama 2 (dua) hari" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "membaptiskan anaknya, dibayar untuk selama 2 (dua) hari," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "isteri melahirkan atau keguguran kandungan, dibayar untuk selama 2 (dua) hari:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "suami/isteri, orang tua/mertua atau anak atau menantu meninggal dunia, dibayar untuk selama 2 (dua) hari, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "anggota keluarga dalam satu rumah meninggal dunia, dibayar untuk selama 1 (satu) hari." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/4/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengaturan pelaksanaan ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) ditetapkan dalam perjanjian kerja, peraturan perusahaan, atau perjanjian kerja bersama." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94> legal:pasalHasKey 94 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal komponen upah terdiri dari upah pokok dan tunjangan tetap maka besarnya upah pokok sedikit-dikitnya 75 96 (tujuh puluh lima perseratus) dari jumlah upah pokok dan tunjangan tetap." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/94/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95> legal:pasalHasKey 95 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pelanggaran yang dilakukan oleh pekerja/buruh karena kesengajaan atau kelalaiannya dapat dikenakan denda." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengusaha yang karena kesengajaan atau kelalaiannya mengakibatkan keterlambatan pembayaran upah, dikenakan denda sesuai dengan persentase tertentu dari upah pekerja/buruh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemerintah mengatur pengenaan denda kepada pengusaha dan/atau pekerja/buruh, dalam pembayaran upah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal perusahaan dinyatakan pailit atau dilikuidasi berdasarkan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku, maka upah dan hak-hak lainnya dari pekerja/buruh merupakan utang yang didahulukan pem- bayarannya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/95/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96> legal:pasalHasKey 96 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tuntutan pembayaran upah pekerja/buruh dan segala pembayaran yang timbul dari hubungan kerja menjadi kadaluwarsa setelah melampaui jangka waktu 2 (dua) tahun sejak timbulnya hak." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/96/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97> legal:pasalHasKey 97 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai penghasilan yang layak, kebijakan pengupahan, kebutuhan hidup layak, dan perlindungan pengupahan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 88, penetapan upah minimum sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 89, dan pengenaan denda sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 95 ayat (1), ayat (2) dan ayat (3) diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/97/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98> legal:pasalHasKey 98 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk memberikan saran, pertimbangan, dan merumuskan kebijakan pengupahan yang akan ditetapkan oleh pemerintah, serta untuk pengembangan sistem pengupahan nasional dibentuk Dewan Pengupahan Nasional, Provinsi, dan Kabupaten/Kota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Keanggotaan Dewan Pengupahan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) terdiri dari unsur pemerintah, organisasi pengusaha, serikat pekerja/-serikat buruh, perguruan tinggi, dan pakar." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Keanggotaan Dewan Pengupahan tingkat Nasional diangkat dan diberhentikan oleh Presiden, sedangkan keanggotaan Dewan Pengupahan Provinsi, Kabupaten/Kota diangkat dan diberhentikan oleh Gubenur/ Bupati/Walikota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara pembentukan, komposisi keanggotaan, tata cara pengangkatan dan pemberhentian keanggotaan, serta tugas dan tata kerja Dewan Pengupahan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (2), diatur dengan Keputusan Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/98/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Ketiga Kesejahteraan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/10/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99> legal:pasalHasKey 99 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh dan keluarganya berhak untuk memperoleh jaminan sosial tenaga kerja." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Jaminan sosial tenaga kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), dilaksanakan sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/99/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100> legal:pasalHasKey 100 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk meningkatkan kesejahteraan bagi pekerja/buruh dan keluarganya, pengusaha wajib menyediakan fasilitas kesejahteraan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyediaan fasilitas kesejahteraan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), dilaksanakan dengan memperhatikan kebutuhan pekerja/buruh dan ukuran kemampuan perusahaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai Jenis dan kriteria fasilitas kesejahteraan sesuai dengan kebutuhan pekerja/buruh dan ukuran kemampuan perusahaan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (2), diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/100/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101> legal:pasalHasKey 101 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk meningkatkan kesejahteraan pekerja/buruh, dibentuk koperasi pekerja/buruh dan usaha-usaha produktif di perusahaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemerintah, pengusaha, dan pekerja/buruh atau serikat pekerja/serikat buruh berupaya menumbuhkembangkan koperasi pekerja/buruh, dan mengembangkan usaha produktif sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembentukan koperasi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), dilaksanakan sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Upaya-upaya untuk menumbuhkembangkan koperasi pekerja/buruh sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2), diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab> legal:babSetHasBab <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11> legal:babHasKey 11 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11> legal:babHasTitle "HUBUNGAN INDUSTRIAL" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11> legal:babHasBagianSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kesatu Umum" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/1> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102> legal:pasalHasKey 102 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam melaksanakan hubungan industrial, pemerintah mempunyai fungsi menetapkan kebijakan, memberikan pelayanan, — melaksanakan pengawasan, dan melakukan penindakan terhadap pelanggaran peraturan perundang-undangan ketenagakerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam melaksanakan hubungan industrial, pekerja/buruh dan serikat pekerja/serikat buruhnya mempunyai fungsi menjalankan pekerjaan sesuai dengan kewajibannya, menjaga ketertiban demi kelangsungan produksi, menyalurkan aspirasi secara demokratis, mengembangkan keterampilan, dan keahliannya serta ikut memajukan perusahaan dan memperjuangkan kesejahteraan anggota beserta keluarganya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam melaksanakan hubungan industrial, pengusaha dan organisasi pengusahanya mempunyai fungsi menciptakan kemitraan, mengembang- kan usaha, memperluas lapangan kerja, dan memberikan kesejahteraan pekerja/buruh secara terbuka, demokratis, dan berkeadilan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/102/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103> legal:pasalHasKey 103 .
