<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Hubungan Industrial dilaksanakan melalui sarana :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "serikat pekerja/serikat buruh," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "organisasi pengusaha," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString ". lembaga kerja sama bipartit," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "embaga kerja sama tripartit," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "peraturan perusahaan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "perjanjian kerja bersama," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "peraturan perundang-undangan ketenagakerjaan: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "lembaga penyelesaian perselisihan hubungan industrial." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/h> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/103/version/0/point/h/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kedua Serikat Pekerja/Serikat Buruh" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104> legal:pasalHasKey 104 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pekerja/buruh berhak membentuk dan menjadi anggota serikat pekerja/serikat buruh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam melaksanakan fungsi sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 102, serikat pekerja/serikat buruh ber-hak menghimpun dan mengelola keuangan serta mempertanggungjawabkan keuangan organisasi termasuk dana mogok." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Besarnya dan tata cara pemungutan dana mogok sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) diatur dalam ang-garan dasar dan/atau anggaran rumah tangga serikat pekerja/serikat buruh yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/104/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Ketiga Organisasi Pengusaha" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105> legal:pasalHasKey 105 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0> .
