<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap pengusaha berhak membentuk dan menjadi anggota organisasi pengusaha." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai organisasi pengusaha diatur sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang ber-laku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/105/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Keempat Lembaga Kerja Sama Bipartit" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106> legal:pasalHasKey 106 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap perusahaan yang mempekerjakan 50 (lima puluh) orang pekerja/ buruh atau lebih wajib membentuk lembaga kerja sama bipartit." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga kerja sama bipartit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) berfungsi sebagai forum komunikasi, dan konsultasi mengenai hal ketenagakerjaan di perusahaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Susunan keanggotaan lembaga kerja sama bipartit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (2) terdiri dari unsur pengusaha dan unsur pekerja/buruh yang ditunjuk oleh pekerja/buruh secara demokratis untuk mewakili kepentingan pekerja/buruh di perusahaan yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan mengenai tata cara pembentukan dan susunan keanggotaan lembaga kerja sama bipartit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) dan ayat (3) diatur dengan Keputusan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/5> legal:bagianHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/5> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kelima Lembaga Kerja Sama Tripartit" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/5> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107> legal:pasalHasKey 107 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga kerja sama tripartit memberikan pertimbangan, saran, dan pendapat kepada pemerintah dan pihak terkait dalam penyusunan kebijakan dan pemecahan masalah ketenagakerjaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga Kerja sama Tripartit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1), terdiri dari :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga Kerja sama Tripartit Nasional, Provinsi, dan Kabupaten/ Kota: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga Kerja sama Tripartit Sektoral Nasional, Provinsi, dan Kabupaten/Kota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Keanggotaan Lembaga Kerja sama Tripartit terdiri dari unsur pemerintah, organisasi pengusaha, dan seri-kat pekerja/serikat buruh." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tata kerja dan susunan organisasi Lembaga Kerja sama Tripartit sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) diatur dengan Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/107/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/6> legal:bagianHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/6> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Keenam Peraturan Perusahaan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/11/bagian/6> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/108> .
