<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h> legal:pointHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "masa kerja 7 (tujuh) tahun atau lebih tetapi kurang dari 8 (delapan) tahun, 8 (delapan) bulan upah," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1> .
