<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "masa kerja 8 (delapan) tahun atau lebih, 9 (sembilan) bulan upah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/2/point/h/point/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Perhitungan uang penghargaan masa kerja sebagaimana dimaksud dalam ayat (1) ditetapkan sebagai be-rikut :" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/156/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
