<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/16> legal:babHasTitle "KETENTUAN PIDANA DAN SANKSI ADMINISTRATIF" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/16> legal:babHasBagianSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/bab/16/bagian> .
