<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/9/text> legal:textHasTextString "Undang-undang Nomor 3 Tahun 1958 tentang Penempatan Tenaga Asing (Lembaran Negara Tahun 1958 Nomor 8 )," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/9> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/9/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/10> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/10> legal:pointHasKey "10" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/10/text> legal:textHasTextString "Undang-undang Nomor 8 Tahun 1961 tentang Wajib Kerja Sarjana (Lembaran Negara Tahun 1961 Nomor 207, Tambahan Lembaran Negara Nomor 2270)," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/10> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/10/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/11> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/11> legal:pointHasKey "11" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/11/text> legal:textHasTextString "Undang undang Nomor 7 Pnps Tahun 1963 tentang Pencegahan Pemogokan dan/atau Penutupan (Lock Out) Di Perusahaan, Jawatan, dan Badan Yang Vital (Lembaran Negara Tahun 1963 Nomor 67)," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/11> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/11/text> .
