<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/12> legal:pointHasKey "12" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/12/text> legal:textHasTextString "Undang undang Nomor 14 Tahun 1969 tentang Ketentuan ketentuan Pokok Mengenai Tenaga Kerja (Lembaran Negara Tahun 1969 Nomor 55, Tambahan Lembaran Negara Nomor 2912)," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/12> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/12/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/192/version/0/point/13> .
